OL,3,CArchibald 'hopeful' of extra #200m to
OL,4,Callocate to ministers in June
OL,6,FFinance Minister Caoimhe Archibald has
OL,7,Fsaid she is hopeful that she will have
OL,8,Faround #200 million in additional
OL,9,Ffunding to allocate to Stormont
OL,10,Fdepartments this month.
OL,12,FHowever, Ms Archibald told MLAs that
OL,13,Fboth the amount and the timing of the
OL,14,Fextra cash was uncertain due to
OL,15,FParliament being prorogued for the
OL,16,FGeneral Election.
