OL,3,CArchibald 'hopeful' of extra #200m to
OL,4,Callocate to ministers in June
OL,6,FDuring ministerial question time, Ms
OL,7,FArchibald faced a number of questions
OL,8,Fabout funding for public services, and
OL,9,Fsaid she believed the public wanted to
OL,10,Fsee the powersharing Executive bring
OL,11,Fits case to Westminster for additional
OL,12,Fmonies with a "unified voice".
OL,14,FLast week the Stormont Assembly backed
OL,15,Fa budget that Ms Archibald conceded
OL,16,Fsaw no ministers getting the funding
OL,17,Fthey had requested.
