OL,3,CArchibald 'hopeful' of extra #200m to
OL,4,Callocate to ministers in June
OL,6,FHowever, the then Ulster Unionist
OL,7,FHealth Minister Robin Swann and his
OL,8,Fparty voted against the spending plan
OL,9,Flast week, warning it would have
OL,10,F"catastrophic" impacts on health
OL,11,Fservices if fully implemented.
OL,13,FMike Nesbitt, who has since replaced
OL,14,Fhis party colleague Mr Swann in the
OL,15,Fhealth portfolio, has sounded similar
OL,16,Falarm.
