OL,3,CArchibald 'hopeful' of extra #200m to
OL,4,Callocate to ministers in June
OL,6,FAsked in the Assembly if all Stormont
OL,7,Fdepartments were facing similar
OL,8,Ffunding pressures, Ms Archibald said:
OL,9,F"We are all aware that over a decade
OL,10,Fof austerity and cuts have been hugely
OL,11,Fdamaging for our public services and
OL,12,Ffor workers, families and communities
OL,13,Fhere.
OL,15,F"It is clear that all departments are
OL,16,Funder significant financial pressure."
OL,18,FShe added: "I think that working
OL,19,Ftogether and having a unified voice
OL,20,Fwill better place us to meet the
OL,21,Fchallenges that we have head-on.
