OL,3,CArchibald 'hopeful' of extra #200m to
OL,4,Callocate to ministers in June
OL,6,F"I want to work with all of my
OL,7,Fministerial colleagues in making the
OL,8,Fcase for more investment in public
OL,9,Fservices.
OL,11,F"I think none of us, either us in here
OL,12,For the public out there are under any
OL,13,Fillusions about the state of our
OL,14,Ffinances but what people want to see
OL,15,Fis leadership and collective working.
OL,16,FThey want to feel that there is some
OL,17,Fhope that things will improve.
OL,19,F"Working with my colleagues in the
OL,20,FExecutive I intend to show that
OL,21,Fleadership."
