OL,3,CArchibald 'hopeful' of extra #200m to
OL,4,Callocate to ministers in June
OL,6,FAlliance Party MLA Nuala McAllister
OL,7,Fasked how much additional money would
OL,8,Fbe available from the June monitoring
OL,9,Fround, where ministers can bid for
OL,10,Fadditional funding made available from
OL,11,Fthe Treasury.
OL,13,FMs Archibald said there would be a
OL,14,Fminimum of #65 million available to
OL,15,Fher.
