OL,3,CArchibald 'hopeful' of extra #200m to
OL,4,Callocate to ministers in June
OL,6,FBut she added: "It is also anticipated
OL,7,Fthere will be significant additional
OL,8,Ffunding arising from Westminster main
OL,9,Festimates, but as these were not
OL,10,Fintroduced before Parliament was
OL,11,Fprorogued, both the timing and the
OL,12,Famount are now uncertain.
OL,14,F"However, I am still hopeful that
OL,15,Fthere will be in the region of #200
OL,16,Fmillion available for allocation in
OL,17,FJune monitoring."
OL,19,FThe SDLP's Matthew O'Toole asked about
OL,20,Fthe greater devolution of more fiscal
OL,21,Fpowers to Stormont.
