OL,3,CArchibald 'hopeful' of extra #200m to
OL,4,Callocate to ministers in June
OL,6,FMs Archibald said: "This is work that
OL,7,Fhas been ongoing for some time, it is
OL,8,Fwork I am committed to taking forward.
OL,10,F"In taking forward any negotiations in
OL,11,Frelation to the devolution of fiscal
OL,12,Fpowers we will have to have an
OL,13,FExecutive position.
OL,15,F"I will be bringing recommendations to
OL,16,Fthe Executive and I would like to be
OL,17,Fdoing that as quickly as possible."
